<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <style>
        body { font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; margin: 0; padding: 0; background-color: #f4f7f6; }
        .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 20px auto; background: #ffffff; border-radius: 8px; overflow: hidden; box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.1); }
        .header { background: linear-gradient(135deg, <%= branding.primaryColor %> 0%, #1d4ed8 100%); padding: 40px 20px; text-align: center; color: white; }
        .header img { max-width: 150px; margin-bottom: 20px; filter: brightness(0) invert(1); }
        .content { padding: 40px 30px; }
        .footer { background: #f8fafc; padding: 20px 30px; text-align: center; font-size: 12px; color: #64748b; }
        h1 { margin: 0; font-size: 24px; }
        p { margin: 15px 0; }
        .status-box { background-color: #eff6ff; border: 1px solid #bfdbfe; padding: 15px; border-radius: 4px; color: #1e3a8a; text-align: center; font-weight: 600; font-size: 16px; margin: 20px 0; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <img src="<%= branding.logoUrl %>" alt="<%= branding.schoolName %> Logo" onerror="this.style.display='none'">
            <h1>Student Status Update</h1>
        </div>
        <div class="content">
            <p>Hello,</p>
            <p>This is to inform you that the account status for student <strong><%= studentName %></strong> at <strong><%= branding.schoolName %></strong> has been updated.</p>
            <div class="status-box">
                New Status: <%= statusName %>
            </div>
            <p>If you have any questions regarding this status change, please reach out to the school administration.</p>
            <p style="margin-top: 30px; border-top: 1px solid #e2e8f0; padding-top: 20px; font-size: 13px; color: #64748b;">
                Thank you,<br>
                School Administration Support Team
            </p>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            <p>© <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> <%= branding.schoolName %>. All rights reserved.</p>
            <p>Powered by CampusConnect</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
